#feed
responds :missing when given a bad format0.10099s
responds :missing when given a bad type0.00674s
without format parameter
redirects main feed to articles RSS feed0.00508s
redirects comments feed to Comments RSS feed0.04906s
redirects trackbacks feed to TrackbacksController RSS feed0.00538s
redirects category feed to Category RSS feed0.00513s
redirects tag feed to Tag RSS feed0.00494s
with format rss20
redirects main feed to articles RSS feed0.00485s
redirects comments feed to comments RSS feed0.04888s
redirects trackbacks feed to TrackbacksController RSS feed0.00556s
redirects category feed to category RSS feed0.00535s
redirects tag feed to tag RSS feed0.00512s
with format atom10
redirects main feed to articles Atom feed0.04996s
redirects comments feed to comments Atom feed0.00519s
redirects trackbacks feed to TrackbacksController Atom feed0.00507s
redirects category feed to category Atom feed0.00509s
redirects tag feed to tag Atom feed0.00507s
with format atom03
redirects main feed to articles Atom feed0.04938s
for an article
without format parameter
redirects article feed to Article RSS feed0.01998s
with format rss20
redirects the article feed to the article RSS feed0.05176s
with format atom10
redirects the article feed to the article Atom feed0.00694s
